name: Blank Blueprint
description: This Blueprint is still a blank slate. Use it to sketch furniture in someone else's SEKAI.

name: Surplus Blueprint
description: A Blueprint that you already owned. Convert it into another Blueprint in the Converter.

name: Surplus Record
description: A Record that you already owned. Convert it into another Record in the Converter.

name: Film
description: Plastic with a light-sensitive coating. You need this to take photos.

name: Blueprint Scrap
description: A torn fragment of a Blueprint. Gather enough of them to make a random Blueprint in the Converter.
